#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today's topic is about family budgets.\n"
"\n"
"Many families are stressed about money, especially if teens keep asking for things!\n"
"\n"
"When we make a budget together, we can agree how to spend AND save to prevent stress and work towards our familyâ€™s goals."
msgstr ""
"Mada ya leo inahusu bajeti za familia.\n"
"\n"
"Familia nyingi hufadhaika kuhusu pesa, hasa ikiwa vijana wanaendelea kuomba vitu!\n"
"\n"
"Tunapopanga bajeti pamoja, tunaweza kukubaliana jinsi ya kutumia na kuweka akiba ili kuzuia mfadhaiko na kufanyia kazi malengo ya familia yetu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings, everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Today's topic is family budgeting.\n"
"\n"
"It is important to create a budget, but it is even more important to create a budget involving the entire family.\n"
"\n"
"Doing it together helps increase the level of understanding of how you spend money as a family and how much you save for the family and you can even come up with plans of how you can save as a family."
msgstr ""
"Habari, zenu.\n"
"\n"
"Mada ya leo ni kuhusu bajeti za familia.\n"
"\n"
"Ni muhimu kupanga bajeti, lakini ni muhimu zaidi kupanga bajeti inayohusisha familia nzima.\n"
"\n"
"Kufanya hivyo pamoja kunasaidia kuongeza kiwango cha uelewa wa jinsi mnavyotumia pesa kama familia na kiasi gani mnaweka akiba kwa ajili ya familia na mnaweza hata kupanga mipango ya jinsi mnavyoweza kuweka akiba mkiwa kama familia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When we involve our teens in budgeting, they learn to be responsible with money and work towards goals. That is something we all want for our teens, right?"
msgstr "Tunapowashirikisha vijana wetu katika kupanga bajeti, wanajifunza kuwajibika na pesa na kufanya kazi kwa malengo. Hilo ni jambo ambalo sote tunataka kwa vijana wetu, sivyo?"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name
#.      @data.characters.f2_son_15.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I have been taking care of my grandchildren, @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name and @data.characters.f2_son_15.name, since their parents died when they were young. We often struggle with money, as I only receive a small grant."
msgstr "Nimekuwa nikiwatunza wajukuu zangu, @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name na @data.characters.f2_son_15.name, tangu wazazi wao wafariki walipokuwa wadogo. Mara nyingi tunahangaika na pesa, kwani mimi hupokea ruzuku ndogo tu."

