#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This week's home practice is to make a budget again - this time WITH your teen and family!\n"
"\n"
"This is an important and fun thing to do with your family - it takes about 30 minutes."
msgstr ""
"Mazoezi ya nyumbani ya wiki hii ni kutengeneza bajeti tena - wakati huu PAMOJA na kijana na familia yako!\n"
"\n"
"Hili ni jambo muhimu na la kufurahisha kufanya na familia yako - inachukua kama dakika 30."

