#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you make a budget with your family this week?"
msgstr "Je, unaweza kupanga bajeti na familia yako wiki hii?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ndiyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Wonderful! Making a family budget is a powerful way to set goals and reduce stress together. Keep it simple and celebrate every small success"
msgstr "Ajabu! Kupanga bajeti ya familia ni njia nzuri ya kuweka malengo pamoja na kupunguza mfadhaiko. Ifanye nyepesi na kusherehekea kila mafanikio madogo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Nafikiri hivyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thatâ€™s a great start! Even talking about money as a family is a big step. Take it one conversation at a time - you are building important skills together."
msgstr "Hiyo ni mwanzo mzuri sana! Hata kuzungumza kuhusu pesa kama familia ni hatua kubwa. Kufanya mazungumzo haya hatua kwa hatua â€“ mnajenga ujuzi muhimu pamoja."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hapana"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay. Budgeting can feel difficult at first. Try starting with one small thing, like planning how to spend this weekâ€™s food money, and build from there."
msgstr "Hiyo ni sawa. Bajeti inaweza kuwa ngumu mwanzoni. Jaribu kuanza na jambo moja dogo, kama kupanga jinsi ya kutumia pesa za chakula za wiki hii, na ujenge kutoka hapo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When we involve teens in budgeting, they learn important life skills, like understanding the difference between needs and wants.\n"
"\n"
"Making a budget together also helps teens see that we all need to make hard choices sometimes, but that it helps us to have enough money at the end of the month - and to realise our goals!"
msgstr ""
"Tunapohusisha vijana katika kupanga bajeti, wanajifunza stadi muhimu za maisha, kama vile kuelewa tofauti kati ya mahitaji na matamanio!\n"
"\n"
"Kutengeneza bajeti pamoja pia huwasaidia vijana kuona kwamba sote tunahitaji kufanya maamuzi magumu wakati mwingine, lakini hutusaidia kuwa na pesa za kutosha mwishoni mwa mwezi - na kutimiza malengo yetu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can creating family budgets help your family? Tap play to learn more"
msgstr "Je, kuunda bajeti za familia kunaweza kusaidia familia yako? Gusa cheza ili upate maelezo zaidi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"I used to ask my mom to buy me nice clothes all the time. Each time, she would say â€œI do not have money,â€ but I knew that she was getting money from my uncle. I did not understand why she refused to buy me clothes. I thought at some point â€œshe does not love me.â€\n"
"\n"
"But one day, she called me to sit down with her and asked â€œwhat are the needs and wants in our house.â€ I started to list all my needs and wants. Then my mother helped me to also think about the family needs. Now I understand where our money is going, towards the things we need as a family.\n"
"\n"
"From that day, I understand I cannot come in and ask any time. Now, when I want something, I wait till the month-end when we all discuss the budget together to see if it fits. We understand each other better now."
msgstr ""
"Nilikuwa nikimwomba mama yangu aninunulie nguo nzuri kila wakati. Kila mara, alikuwa akisema â€œSina pesa,â€ lakini nilijua kwamba alikuwa akipata pesa kutoka kwa mjomba wangu. Sikuelewa kwanini alikataa kuninunulia nguo. Nilifikiri wakati fulani â€œhanipendi.â€\n"
"\n"
"Lakini siku moja, aliniita niketi naye na kuniuliza â€œni mahitaji gani na matakwa gani katika nyumba yetu.â€ Nilianza kuorodhesha mahitaji na matakwa yangu yote. Kisha mama yangu akanisaidia pia kufikiria kuhusu mahitaji ya familia. Sasa ninaelewa pesa zetu zinaenda wapi, kuelekea vitu tunavyohitaji kama familia.\n"
"\n"
"Kuanzia siku hiyo, naelewa siwezi kuja na kuuliza wakati wowote. Sasa, ninapotaka kitu, nasubiri hadi mwisho wa mwezi tutakapojadili bajeti pamoja ili kuona kama inafaa. Tunaelewana vizuri zaidi sasa."

